com.baasbox.android

Class BaasApiException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.baasbox.android.BaasException
          • com.baasbox.android.BaasApiException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaasClientException, BaasServerException

    public class BaasApiException
extends BaasException
    A subclass of BaasException. This is the root of all the exception thrown by the remote server; if it crashes or the request made is invalid, a subclass of BaasApiException is thrown by the SDK.
    Since:
    0.7.3
